title: Pallasite Project - Phoenix EP
description: Receiving transmissions from the cosmic over mind and inspired by unconditional love, Pallasite Project music taps into the mysterious, strange, dark & light energies floating around the collective brain. Using 100% hand crafted samples and synthesizer/piano improvisation, Pallasite Project touches on genres that include deep psychedelia, electro, dub, world fusion, and acoustic piano.
